title: Dutch Treat Update A146-155 (Various Rock Symphonys)
description:
Hi, this is probable (also regarding some response) my best upload ever.

Ten new 2-hour playlists for the Dutch Treat Collection. Actually these Ten deserve their own series; only tracks Longer 7 minutes (Brothers in Arms is 7:00). All these (too) long Master Pieces you admire so much and sit on an album somewhere (well most of them). So I looked and found (well a lot of them) and made a few bar-proof playlists.
I'm open for suggestions. 

This Update may contain minor changes and may have been renumbered for accessibility reasons.... Enjoy,
